data.title: Ms. Lundberg's Poetry of the Day
data.meta_description: So, I've started to get a few of you with poems of your own that you thought you might like to share, and I thought to myself, self, why don't you have students write their stuff here? And now we have it; a purpose for the page called the poet's corner. Should you so desire,
